snippet.title: Multiplayer Trailer | Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III
snippet.description:
World Premiere of the #MW3 Multiplayer Trailer.

16 iconic maps modernized for fast-paced combat 🏃

Tune into #CODNext on October 5 for the premiere of live Multiplayer gameplay https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9o2bxsRvvEE 🔥
